V0214_01_00_00_0.text: The headline will read: "Carly Carmine - Duel Champion!"

V0214_01_00_01_0.text: Hold the front page 'cause Carly's getting the scoop!

V0214_01_00_02_0.text: I took some late night Dueling classes, so I know I can win!

V0214_01_00_03_1.text: I hope my Fortune Deck pulls through!

V0214_01_00_04_0.text:
You have to let me write your exclusive!
Pretty please?

V0214_01_00_05_0.text:
If I win, you have to do whatever I ask!
Deal or deal?

V0214_01_00_06_0.text: I'm covering Team 5D's for my profile piece!

V0214_01_00_07_0.text: This is like the Duel between Yusei and the spider guy!

V0214_01_00_08_0.text: As a former member, I'll beat all the Dark Signers!

V0214_01_00_08_1.text: ...Not that I remember being a Dark Signer...

V0214_03_00_00_0.text: I have this in the bag!

V0214_03_00_05_0.text:
Nothing's working...
But maybe it will starting now!

V0214_05_00_00_0.text: You know who's luckier than lucky? Me!

V0214_06_01_00_0.text: You won't get away with that!

V0214_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0214_08_00_00_0.text: I activate the Quick-Play Spell, Unacceptable Result!

V0214_08_00_00_1.text: I Special Summon a Fortune Fairy from my hand!

V0214_08_00_01_0.text: Here's the Continuous Spell, Miracle Stone!

V0214_08_00_02_0.text: Miracle Stone's effect lets me draw a card!

V0214_08_00_03_0.text:
I activate my Spell Card!
Lucky Loan!

V0214_08_00_04_0.text: I'll equip this on my monster!

V0214_08_00_05_0.text: Omega Goggles lets me see your secrets and get the scoop!

V0214_08_00_06_0.text:
This is the card Jack and I used together!
Mind Trust!

V0214_09_00_00_0.text:
My fortune says my luck will be...
Super awesome!

V0214_09_00_01_0.text: Drawing this card allows me to use its effect!

V0214_09_00_03_0.text:
My fortune says my luck will be...
Very awesome!

V0214_09_00_04_0.text: By drawing this Fortune Fairy, I can use its effect!

V0214_09_00_06_0.text:
My fortune says my luck will be...
So-so.

V0214_09_00_07_0.text: I'll use the effect of the Fortune Fairy I just drew!

V0214_09_00_09_0.text:
My fortune says my luck will be...
Kinda bad. Uh oh.

V0214_09_00_09_1.text:
Sigh...
But I can't lose heart!

V0214_09_00_10_0.text: The card I drew is... a Fortune Fairy!

V0214_09_00_12_0.text:
My fortune says my luck will be...
Terrible.

V0214_09_00_12_1.text: Well, that just means I have to fight harder!

V0214_09_00_13_0.text: The card I drew is... this one!

V0214_09_00_15_0.text:
My fortune says my luck will be...
Super mega lame?!?

V0214_09_00_16_0.text:
This card's a downer... but whatever!
I activate its effect!

V0214_09_00_21_0.text:
I tricked you!
Twin-Shield Defender's effect activates!

V0214_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0214_13_00_01_0.text:
Her lucky number is 1!
Her lucky color is yellow!

V0214_13_00_02_0.text: She has a light-up charm that makes wishes come true!

V0214_13_00_04_0.text:
Her lucky number is 2!
Her lucky color is red!

V0214_13_00_05_0.text: She has a lucky goldfish that spreads joy!

V0214_13_00_07_0.text:
Her lucky number is 3!
Her lucky color is green!

V0214_13_00_08_0.text: Her lucky plant helps her find missing objects!

V0214_13_00_10_0.text:
Her lucky number is 4!
Her lucky color is blue!

V0214_13_00_11_0.text: She points her umbrella to the east for luck!

V0214_13_00_13_0.text:
Her lucky number is 5!
Her lucky color is purple!

V0214_13_00_14_0.text: With her lucky sunglasses, she can find lost items!

V0214_13_00_15_0.text:
I give you...
Fortune Fairy Chee!

V0214_13_00_16_0.text:
Her lucky number is 6!
Her lucky color is black!

V0214_13_00_17_0.text: Her lucky boots help me outrun the competition!

V0214_13_00_22_1.text:
It reminds me when Jack and I teamed up...
*blush*

V0214_13_00_24_0.text: Jack uses this Tuner Monster too!

V0214_13_00_25_0.text:
I can use your help, Jack!
Twin-Shield Defender!

V0214_37_00_00_0.text: As Jack roars, feel the crushing blow of victory!

V0214_37_00_00_1.text:
Synchrooooo Summon!
...Yay! I got to say it!

V0214_20_00_01_0.text: Umm... I guess I'll Set a card.

V0214_21_00_00_0.text: That's only a teaser of what I can do!

V0214_28_00_00_0.text: I should be in the headline instead of the byline!

V0214_28_00_01_0.text:
Don't worry.
I'll keep your ID secret when I write my story.

V0214_28_00_02_0.text: My fortune said I'd be super happy today - and it came true!

V0214_28_00_03_0.text: You thought I'd be easy to defeat, but you were way wrong!

V0214_28_00_03_1.text:
Cuz I'm Jack's future wife!
...Don't tell him I said that.

V0214_28_00_04_0.text: I'm one step closer to achieving my dream!

V0214_28_00_04_1.text: Where our kids are Dueling champions!

V0214_28_00_05_0.text:
Jack!
You promised that I'd get an exclusive!

V0214_28_00_06_0.text: I can't believe I used to be one of you.

V0214_28_00_06_1.text: Good thing memories of those times are fuzzy.

V0214_29_00_00_0.text:
Argh!
You won't get me next time!

V0214_29_00_02_0.text: My fortune did say I'd be sad today...

V0214_29_00_03_0.text: Maybe I'm better at rooting for my friends than Dueling...

V0214_29_00_04_0.text: I wrote an article that says how awesome you are!

V0214_29_00_04_1.text: If only the editor would publish it...

V0214_29_00_05_0.text:
The Dark Signers are tough!
And I used to be one of them?

V0214_33_00_00_0.text: I won't let a scoop pass me by!

V0214_30_00_01_0.text: You can't fight when you're hungry.

V0214_30_00_02_0.text: You may look like a Duelist, but you're not one.

V0214_34_00_00_0.text: W-Wait! I still want the scoop!

V0214_34_00_02_0.text: You're a hard worker. I like that.

V0214_34_00_04_0.text:
...Super awesome!
All your wishes will come true!

V0214_34_00_06_0.text:
...So-so.
But you might find something you lost.

V0214_34_00_07_0.text:
...Kinda bad.
But you may get lucky if you face the east.

V0214_34_00_09_0.text:
...Super mega lame!
Your rivals will get the upper hand!

V0214_35_00_00_0.text:
I'm Carly the reporter!
Nice to meet you!

V0214_36_00_05_0.text:
I'm sorry, Jack.
If only I was a better teammate...

V0214_26_00_01_0.text: I still have a lot of Duel left!

V0214_38_00_00_0.text:
Ready... Set... Duel!
Yay! I got to say it!
